		(property "Description" "Omron G6K-2F-Y DC12, SMD DPDT signal relay (2 Form C), 12V coil ~1.315k. Used as SPDT: coil pin1=P4 (+), pin8=P1; pole-1 COM=3, NO=4->P4, NC=2 open; pole-2 5/6/7 spare. On-board WF26 latch: Türruf-pulsed (~1s), then sealed in from the P2 supply; flyback D1 on the coil."
